{
  "texts": [
    "One of the most vital disadvantages is that without the combination with other fine-tuned language models, it cannot identify the type of previous posts by a particular label.",
    "Hence, the participants' posts can only be selected by which phase they were raised, but not a clear classification result.",
    "Also, it can only switch to another discussion phase depending on the time or the number of participants' posts, but not both.",
    "To improve these points is in our future work.",
    "To further improve the quality of discussions, other kinds of agents will be designed and implemented based on this framework in the future.Fig. 55Fig."
  ]
}